  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct intended for lumbar spinal fixation in adult patients. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two independent laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors are assessed; one factor (Test conditions) falls below the required level due to a single test condition being evaluated. Decision: Accepted at Medium assurance for the intended regulatory submission context.",
